{"tid":1572346,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］ 如何運動時不受傷","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:44:35.000Z","uid":282957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d93cb79f26511a5d5e3d0d56e427a6a9310c0179","tid":1572346,"uid":282957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"我係廢柴物理治療師有錯，更正一下我<br />\n我想教下大家點樣做運動時不受傷<br />\n<br />\n第一：<br />\n詳細可以睇返警棍使用守則：<br />\n其實人嘅關節同胸骨係好脆弱<br />\n所以大家做運動要唔好比<span style=\"font-size: large;\">硬物同其他人嘅體重</span>撞到呢啲位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjrMWNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjrMWNz.jpg&h=52b91d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uhcSt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uhcSt9.jpg&h=db3532f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n胸骨嚴重受傷係有機會死嫁<br />\n但係如果情況輕啲打到啲肌肉<br />\n可以連呼吸/咳都痛<br />\n到時唔好話做運動<br />\n過馬路行快啲都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n第二：<br />\n好多時喺關節完全伸直嘅時間因為筋肉收緊咗所以有一定保護作用 <br />\n所以關節微彎嘅時間係比較脆弱嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WGk1ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WGk1ef.jpg&h=5f13a057&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上人嘅皮膚下面有脂肪<br />\n脂肪係人嘅避震器<br />\n所以撞到骨係痛好多嫁 <br />\n要記住好好保護骨頭少肉嘅位置 <span style=\"color: red;\">例如腳踝，上五寸下五寸，膝蓋，膝頭側，手腕手肘。</span><br />\n<br />\n下圖係膝頭哥關節<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ob8Pag2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fob8Pag2.jpg&h=4a0caaef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紫色位置係比較少肉嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n理論講咁多 一個例子講解一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8GLJp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8GLJp.jpg&h=98855b26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n假設呢位先生喺街跑緊步跌倒<br />\n但呢個時間紅色箭咀嘅方向嘅力量撞埋去<br />\n咁佢嘅關節就可能有嚴重嘅傷害/殘廢<br />\n同埋一個人仆親好時會打側瞓 <br />\n呢個時間如果有力量對準近地下嘅手/腳受傷通常會更嚴重<br />\n就算行得返都有排復康 好危險<br />\n所以大家做運動要小心啲<br />\n好好咁保護關節位置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我希望可以全民開心做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c753dabad905a86a88032a3ac8c50b3db54e03d","tid":1572346,"uid":282957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WBpJC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WBpJC2.jpg&h=9c8ba704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n補圖"},{"pid":"276904dd0a2b8eadf9f0680f829ece1fd5f22cfb","tid":1572346,"uid":282957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q46Umqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ46Umqd.jpg&h=4de70d1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f23746b5cfaf2e3ebeb718473a39596339aa0c6","tid":1572346,"uid":282957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"開錯台 sor 9"},{"pid":"e6a54dbd134466dedc4d8f0b0f44fa741fe398a3","tid":1572346,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"dbf6afb42e4cb0f91e0e9fb3fd04f56c0fa8df2a","tid":1572346,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93cb79f26511a5d5e3d0d56e427a6a9310c0179","tid":1572346,"uid":282957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"我係廢柴物理治療師有錯，更正一下我<br />\n我想教下大家點樣做運動時不受傷<br />\n<br />\n第一：<br />\n詳細可以睇返警棍使用守則：<br />\n其實人嘅關節同胸骨係好脆弱<br />\n所以大家做運動要唔好比<span style=\"font-size: large;\">硬物同其他人嘅體重</span>撞到呢啲位置<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjrMWNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjrMWNz.jpg&h=52b91d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uhcSt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uhcSt9.jpg&h=db3532f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br